g":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7e3cad5df0cf1fbe9523bbe7b15ffec021afa0ee","tid":495804,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T11:35:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6e21290f2a3bb6bdc46890e3428a44ecac834d7","tid":495804,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T11:38:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e9a9d185b6272b96a6f0fcc0745a1b5e6dfa339","tid":495804,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T11:44:42.000Z","msg":"【終極一戰】修改議事規則已經殺到埋身，我哋一定唔會坐以待斃，議會內必定會用盡一切方法去阻止，而議會外更加需要市民支持。由今晚開始，民主派將會舉行包圍立法會行動，紮營留守立法會廣場。希望市民能夠到場支持，務求集結民氣，推倒修改議案！<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/11/194135_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F11%2F194135_d0b3244693f743a542dc6a84b8f5ae22.jpg&h=dad7cc2b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"df6ced3ccfdd915210391c3d25c405d521d13cf0","tid":495804,"uid":28366,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-12T02:55:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}